<h2 id="for-linux">For Linux</h2>

<h3 id="download-nvim-for-linux-from-source">Download nvim for linux from Source</h3>

<ul>
  <li>curl -LO https://github.com/neovim/neovim/releases/latest/download/nvim.appimage</li>
  <li>chmod u+x nvim.appimage</li>
  <li>
    <p>./nvim.appimage</p>
  </li>
  <li>./nvim.appimage ‚Äìappimage-extract</li>
  <li>./squashfs-root/AppRun ‚Äìversion</li>
  <li>mv squashfs-root /</li>
  <li>ln -s /squashfs-root/AppRun /usr/bin/nvim</li>
  <li>nvim</li>
</ul>

<h3 id="install-packer-from-source">Install Packer from source</h3>

<blockquote>
  <p>git clone ‚Äìdepth 1 https://github.com/wbthomason/packer.nvim/ $(pwd)/site/pack/packer/start/packer.nvim</p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>git clone ‚Äìbranch master https://github.com/CompanyDATV/neovim ~.config\nvim ‚Äìdepth 1</p>
</blockquote>

<p>or</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>git clone https://codeberg.org/nulldoot2k/Neovim-Lua.git ~/.config/nvim/.</p>
</blockquote>

<p>After : nvim Type <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">:PackerSync</code></p>

